data.meta_description: Prince Olav of Norway arrives with best man, Duke of York. The King and Queen of Norway and Princess Ingesbourg arrive. Princess Martha, neice of King of Sweden, her father and Prince Karl arrive. Scene of the bride and groom leaving together. A Laplander in a four-point hat speaks to camera about wedding. Crowds gather in the streets.
